#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:2
#: f9299d395b664ce7be442be66333ddec
msgid "Geomechanics: Drucker-Prager triaxial compression"
msgstr "岩土力学：Drucker-Prager 三轴压缩"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:4
#: 11222677ced54716a84d368ffd26bad6
msgid ""
"This example introduces a small geomechanics application inside the solid-"
"mechanics example family.  It implements an example-only Drucker-Prager "
"plasticity assembler for a pressure-dependent soil or weak-rock material and"
" drives it through a simple triaxial-compression strain path."
msgstr ""
"本示例在固体力学示例系列中介绍了一个小型岩土力学应用。它针对一种压力相关的土体或软岩材料，实现了一个仅作示例用的 Drucker-Prager "
"塑性装配器，并通过一条简单的三轴压缩应变路径进行驱动。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:9
#: 9ea68c48c2274b00a6047850efde1c10
msgid ""
"The goal is deliberately modest: demonstrate TensorMesh conventions for "
"geomechanics without adding a public API.  The local assembler lives in "
"``examples/solid/geomechanics/drucker_prager_triaxial/drucker_prager_triaxial.py``."
msgstr ""
"目标有意保持简单：在不增加公共 API 的前提下，演示 TensorMesh 在岩土力学中的使用约定。局部装配器位于 "
"``examples/solid/geomechanics/drucker_prager_triaxial/drucker_prager_triaxial.py``\\"
" 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:14
#: e98f084760e941b7b3f447820d37e783
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:16
#: d1151108e9234e578c58fafc39d7759a
msgid ""
"The model is small-strain, associated Drucker-Prager plasticity with linear "
"isotropic hardening.  TensorMesh keeps the internal solid-mechanics "
"convention stress tension-positive.  For geomechanics reporting, the script "
"prints axial stress and mean pressure as compression-positive quantities."
msgstr ""
"模型为小应变、关联 Drucker-Prager 塑性，并带有线性各向同性硬化。TensorMesh "
"内部保持固体力学约定：应力以受拉为正。为便于岩土力学报告，脚本将轴向应力和平均压力以受压为正的形式输出。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:21
#: 880edccf9dee4d95bdad74f8f21fd431
msgid "The yield function is written internally as"
msgstr "屈服函数在内部写为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:23
#: 7bb9d5bca3284c029b9ae72376ac61b1
msgid "f(\\sigma, \\alpha) = q + \\eta I_1 - (k + H\\alpha) \\le 0,"
msgstr "f(\\sigma, \\alpha) = q + \\eta I_1 - (k + H\\alpha) \\le 0,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:27
#: 21eadc3dc1ba48b0b9f40f4db36d4012
msgid "where"
msgstr "其中"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:29
#: 807e96d7ad8a47248c4608b4ff3c3140
msgid ""
"I_1 = \\mathrm{tr}(\\sigma), \\qquad\n"
"q = \\sqrt{\\frac{3}{2}\\,s:s}, \\qquad\n"
"p = -\\frac{I_1}{3}."
msgstr ""
"I_1 = \\mathrm{tr}(\\sigma), \\qquad\n"
"q = \\sqrt{\\frac{3}{2}\\,s:s}, \\qquad\n"
"p = -\\frac{I_1}{3}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:35
#: 03dd1c226e8f487ab0f9376e3667cf3c
msgid ""
"Because compression gives negative ``I1`` in the tension-positive "
"convention, higher confinement lowers ``f`` and delays yielding."
msgstr "由于在受拉为正约定下受压会导致 ``I1`` 为负，更高的围压会降低 ``f`` 并延迟屈服。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:39
#: ff1eb9b6dd2a4c038fd1e547a552bb3f
msgid "History variables"
msgstr "历史变量"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:41
#: 9e98d9dfde9e44be97c96b763569ed98
msgid ""
"The example follows the same pattern as the existing J2 plasticity example:"
msgstr "本示例遵循现有 J2 塑性示例的相同模式："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:43
#: 84cf6eb5a20949f5804aa991b465ef2c
msgid ""
"per-quadrature history variables are stored in ``self.history[etype]``;"
msgstr "逐求积点的历史变量存储在 ``self.history[etype]`` 中；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:44
#: e9969a1ad4f6480ea27848e732825142
msgid ""
"previous-step ``eps_p`` and ``alpha`` are passed through ``element_data``;"
msgstr "上一步的 ``eps_p`` 和 ``alpha`` 通过 ``element_data`` 传递；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:45
#: 7aa3214f128b4e699529f91195289895
msgid ""
"``update_state(u)`` is called after each converged load step under "
"``torch.no_grad()``."
msgstr "``update_state(u)`` 在每个收敛的载荷步结束后，于 ``torch.no_grad()`` 上下文中被调用。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:48
#: 430868300bb64032a8a4d27d1c5823d7
msgid ""
"The example remains local to the script so the public API can be discussed "
"after the convention-setting example has been reviewed."
msgstr "本示例仅保留在脚本内部，以便在确立约定的示例经过审阅后，再讨论公共 API。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:52
#: bbbde41046494e61a0acb94966bcd715
msgid "Sanity check"
msgstr "合理性检验"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:54
#: 4d64c215fba04414acdd73b91b91bfe1
msgid "Two confinement levels are run:"
msgstr "运行两种围压水平："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:56
#: 1bb6792689064fc286591860fd76bb84
msgid "``p0 = 0 kPa``;"
msgstr "``p0 = 0 kPa``\\ ；"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:57
#: a2db93ab73be4269893059981c9d8103
msgid "``p0 = 100 kPa``."
msgstr "``p0 = 100 kPa``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/drucker_prager_triaxial.rst:59
#: 532919342edd471ba17e5225bcd64c2e
msgid ""
"The script checks that the higher-confinement case reaches the elastic trial"
" yield surface later and that the committed plastic history variable is "
"monotonic."
msgstr "脚本验证更高围压的情况更晚到达弹性试探屈服面，且提交的塑性历史变量是单调的。"

